summary: I'm a senior petrophysicist with >13 years experience in the oil and gas industry. My experience covers the full lifecycle of a field: from exploration to field development, well reservoir and field management and abandonment. In recent years I've been exploring the added value of digitalization in the form of automation and data analytics to gain more insights from existing data.
